nd them.\n\nThe commercial ends with a red Safelite van driving down a quiet residential street at dusk, trees and houses on both sides and a pinkish sky overhead. Large white branding fills the center of the screen: “Safelite.” Beneath it, the tagline reads, “Your glass. Your way.” A smaller line below says, “Schedule at safelite.com,” while the van continues away down the road.",
